import requests

def get_horror_movies():
    url = "https://api.themoviedb.org/3/discover/movie"
    params = {
        "api_key": "API_KEY",
        "with_genres": "27",
        "sort_by": "popularity.desc"
    }
    response = requests.get(url, params=params)
    data = response.json()
    movies = []
    for movie in data["results"]:
        movies.append(movie["title"])
    return movies

get_horror_movies()
